{"info": {"author": "Insolita", "author_email": "webmaster100500@ya.ru", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "description": "Console Translator\n==================\n\n### Installation\n\n`pip3 install cli_translate --user`\n\n\n### Features\n\n - Quick translation for text in clipboard\n\n - Ability for replace text in clipboard with translation\n\n - Ability for output with notify-send (useful with hotkey binding)\n\n - Store all translated texts in sqlite database\n\n - Google or Yandex translation clients \n\n### Configure Yandex Api key\n\nThe usage yandex translator require following steps\n\n   - go to https://translate.yandex.ru/developers/keys and register free api key\n\n   - define environment variable with name YANDEX_TRANSLATE_API_KEY and with api key as value [Guide](https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/environment_variables)\n\n\n ### Usage Examples\n\n  - `itrans -to es`  Clipboard text will be translated\n\n  - `itrans -to fr \"Some text\"`  \"Some text\" will be translated\n\n  - `itrans -to en -i` Interactive text input mode\n\n  - `itrans -to en -p` Clipboard text will be translated and replaced with translation\n\n  - `itrans --help`  See All available options\n\n\n ### Tips and Tricks\n  - register bash/zsh aliases with most useful options; example `alias et=\"itrans -to en -p -o -c yandex\"\n\n  - save translation to file `itrans [options] > file.txt`\n\n  - translate text from file `itrans [options] \"$(cat /path/to_file.txt)\"`\n\n  - pipe result to another `itrans --raw \"Hello World\"|cowsay`\n\n### Limitations\n\nThis utility is for personal use, not automated translations. \n\nThe volume of translated text lenght  is limited per-request\n\n### Screens\n\n![Screen1](./img/cli1.png)\n\n![Screen2](./img/cli2.png)\n\n![Screen3](./img/cli3.png)\n\n\n", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "https://github.com/Insolita/cli_translate/tarball/master", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/Insolita/cli_translate", "keywords": "translation,translate,yandex,google,google translate,clipboard,notify-send,console", "license": "MIT", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "cli-translate", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/cli-translate/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/cli-translate/", "project_urls": {"Download": "https://github.com/Insolita/cli_translate/tarball/master", "Homepage": "https://github.com/Insolita/cli_translate"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/cli-translate/0.0.5/", "requires_dist": ["pyperclip (>=1.5.27)", "requests (>=2.18)", "pyquery (>=1.2.9)"], "requires_python": ">=3.4", "summary": "Useful translation tool for console. With features: translate text from clipboard and store translation logs", "version": "0.0.5", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h1>Console Translator</h1>\n<h3>Installation</h3>\n<p><code>pip3 install cli_translate --user</code></p>\n<h3>Features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Quick translation for text in clipboard</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Ability for replace text in clipboard with translation</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Ability for output with notify-send (useful with hotkey binding)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Store all translated texts in sqlite database</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Google or Yandex translation clients</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Configure Yandex Api key</h3>\n<p>The usage yandex translator require following steps</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>go to <a href=\"https://translate.yandex.ru/developers/keys\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://translate.yandex.ru/developers/keys</a> and register free api key</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>define environment variable with name YANDEX_TRANSLATE_API_KEY and with api key as value <a href=\"https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/environment_variables\" rel=\"nofollow\">Guide</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Usage Examples</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>itrans -to es</code>  Clipboard text will be translated</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>itrans -to fr \"Some text\"</code>  \"Some text\" will be translated</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>itrans -to en -i</code> Interactive text input mode</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>itrans -to en -p</code> Clipboard text will be translated and replaced with translation</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>itrans --help</code>  See All available options</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Tips and Tricks</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>register bash/zsh aliases with most useful options; example `alias et=\"itrans -to en -p -o -c yandex\"</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>save translation to file <code>itrans [options] &gt; file.txt</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>translate text from file <code>itrans [options] \"$(cat /path/to_file.txt)\"</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>pipe result to another <code>itrans --raw \"Hello World\"|cowsay</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Limitations</h3>\n<p>This utility is for personal use, not automated translations.</p>\n<p>The volume of translated text lenght  is limited per-request</p>\n<h3>Screens</h3>\n<p><img alt=\"Screen1\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/bbeebb228c1c3eb59d54203d3b53960bebb33574/2e2f696d672f636c69312e706e67\"></p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screen2\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/1b01828e2930978d95e6776fa54cded88c7c7519/2e2f696d672f636c69322e706e67\"></p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screen3\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/7a5ad8568163432e8357ab899e9cf80fc1d7ac72/2e2f696d672f636c69332e706e67\"></p>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 6347265, "releases": {"0.0.2": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "475a77dd11c4b56dba5459931d0899c0", "sha256": "dcc09f7da53351d130dc250bd461ee7a05ec6406bcc0fbcb95f7da40dc0d896e"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "cli_translate-0.0.2-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "475a77dd11c4b56dba5459931d0899c0", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "